22
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:14,220
Don't worry about your mom. I'll take care of her.

23
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:16,630
You need to take good care of yourself.

24
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:19,480
Take it easy. Don't worry.

25
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,470
No matter how hard it might be,

26
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:23,240
