37
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:14,640
I'd be happy.

38
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,170
Coming!

39
00:03:31,970 --> 00:03:34,110
Coming!

40
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:40,790
How come you three all come back together?

41
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:42,470
I have something in the oven.

42
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:44,030
Mom!

43
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:49,270
Lili, what's wrong?

44
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:52,880
- Aunt Li-<br>- Don't.

45
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:59,090
It's all Qianren's fault.

46
00:03:59,090 --> 00:04:02,770
Qianren's company started an initiative to find errors,

47
00:04:02,770 --> 00:04:06,310
He scolded Lili harshly in front of everybody.

48
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:08,590
Of course Lili feels wronged.

49
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:11,460
