53
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:32,050
Sorry, Aunt Li. I was definitely in a bad mood today.

54
00:04:32,050 --> 00:04:35,030
Once this came up, I couldn't control my temper.

55
00:04:35,030 --> 00:04:38,590
