56
00:04:38,590 --> 00:04:42,080
Don't worry. I'll look after her in the future.

57
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,320
I'll never upset her again.

58
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,840
Such a silly child.

59
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:48,050
Wasn't it just criticism on your work?

60
00:04:48,050 --> 00:04:50,260
What's the big deal?

61
00:04:50,260 --> 00:04:54,150
