78
00:06:09,330 --> 00:06:12,340
If I say I wasn't, I'd be lying.

79
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:14,850
But being with her everyday

80
00:06:14,850 --> 00:06:18,490
makes me happy. That's most important.

81
00:06:18,490 --> 00:06:22,610
But, you knew all along about Lili's hereditary history.

82
00:06:22,610 --> 00:06:25,840
You don't mind one bit?

83
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,910
Lili is Aunt Li's daughter.

84
00:06:27,910 --> 00:06:31,770
