89
00:06:48,230 --> 00:06:50,580
I want to take care of Lili.

90
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:53,710
As more than siblings.

91
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:56,570
I want to take care of her for the rest of my life.

92
00:07:05,930 --> 00:07:09,270
If you sincerely and truly mean that,

93
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:11,280
I support you.

94
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:14,970
Thank you, dad.

95
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:26,390
Mom.

96
00:07:27,370 --> 00:07:30,740
It's been a long time since I slept under the same blanket as you.

97
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:36,500
