When your father was alive, I couldn't even cook.

109
00:08:29,810 --> 00:08:33,360
Let alone change a light bulb or fix the water heater.

110
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:38,790
Many times, I thought

111
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:41,830
