115
00:08:58,450 --> 00:09:01,230
And life went on like that.

116
00:09:02,350 --> 00:09:06,920
Sometimes, I think that old saying makes a lot of sense.

117
00:09:08,190 --> 00:09:13,050
Between husband and wife, the first one to leave

118
00:09:13,050 --> 00:09:16,650
