121
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:30,540
I'll be with you a lifetime, we'll never be apart.

122
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:33,440
Whether we go to heaven or hell,

123
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,900
I will always be with you.

124
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:41,250
If I make him watch me

125
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:46,930
