126
00:09:46,930 --> 00:09:50,210
Pei Shangxuan's life become?

127
00:09:50,210 --> 00:09:52,590
Anyway, luckily,

128
00:09:52,590 --> 00:09:56,690
I met Uncle Liu.

129
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:02,910
Unlce Liu is a good person.

130
00:10:04,690 --> 00:10:10,200
Yes. During the most difficult time of my life,

131
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,440
meeting your Uncle Liu

132
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:15,330
