133
00:10:16,690 --> 00:10:21,130
But I'm most grateful for the change in Qianren.

134
00:10:21,130 --> 00:10:25,360
When I got sick this time, he not only found a specialist

135
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:29,000
but brought me medicine. While doing so many nice things,

136
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:32,400
