210
00:18:42,090 --> 00:18:44,270
For this family,

211
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:49,310
for you mom. You must strive to live.

212
00:19:01,530 --> 00:19:05,630
Help me set up going to Beijing.

213
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:15,360
And, before deciding on surgery,

214
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:17,040
besides you and Uncle Liu,

215
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:19,610
