00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,940
Thank you for looking after me.

223
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:55,610
No problem.

224
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:18,160
Yichen, today is my last day at Aochuang. I want-

225
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:21,470
Sister Li, I was looking forward to working with you.

226
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:25,350
I never thought you'd be leaving. It's too sudden, too unbearable.

227
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:29,270
No matter if what you said is true or fake,

228
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:31,160
