229
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:34,540
There's no need to be angry at someone you'll never see again.

230
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:36,900
It's meaningless.

231
00:20:48,930 --> 00:20:52,640
Lili, you're really leaving.

232
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,260
Because I'm transferring for work

233
00:20:54,260 --> 00:20:57,230
