236
00:21:02,630 --> 00:21:05,440
I don't want to.

237
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:10,870
This place will always be reserved for my best friend, Lili.

238
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:16,800
That day you came home drunk scared me.

239
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:19,870
