240
00:21:21,010 --> 00:21:23,280
It's nothing I can't bear.

241
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:38,130
Jun,

242
00:21:39,270 --> 00:21:43,250
You're the most thick-skinned girl I've met ever in my life.

243
00:21:56,190 --> 00:21:58,970
I hope you make full use of this talent

244
00:21:58,970 --> 00:22:01,910
