247
00:22:08,830 --> 00:22:12,090
Boys come and go, best friends are forever.

248
00:22:12,090 --> 00:22:14,560
You're the best.

249
00:22:16,610 --> 00:22:20,120
Oh yeah. If you're going away for work,

250
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:22,540
