444
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:46,420
You're wrong, Li Li.

445
00:39:46,420 --> 00:39:52,120
It's my life's biggest accomplishment to make you smile everyday.

446
00:39:52,120 --> 00:39:57,480
I want to stay by your side forever.

447
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:06,280
