463
00:42:33,770 --> 00:42:39,970
It's all thanks to you and Uncle Liu that we were able to prevent my mother from knowing.

464
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:45,940
If not, she wouldn't have left peacefully.

465
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:51,280
